<emphasis box="[345,418,1470,1496]" italics="true" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">Betula</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Beljaev, E. A." box="[432,588,1470,1497]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" refId="ref91599" refString="Beljaev, E. A. (2016) Fam. Geometridae - Pyadenitzi. In: Lelei, A. S. (Ed.), Annotated catalogue of the insects of Russian Far East. Vol. 2. Lepidoptera. Dal'nauka, Vladivostok, pp. 518 - 666. [in Russian]" type="book" year="2016">Beljaev 2016</bibRefCitation>
