<paragraph blockId="60.[151,1437,1289,1569]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,262,1506,1532]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">Note.</emphasis>
The previous records of 
<taxonomicName authority="Butler, 1878" authorityName="Butler" authorityYear="1878" box="[551,879,1506,1532]" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Lomaspilis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="opis">
<emphasis box="[551,730,1506,1532]" italics="true" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">Lomaspilis opis</emphasis>
Butler, 1878
</taxonomicName>
for the Baikal region likely belong to 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Makhov &amp; Beljaev" authorityYear="2019" box="[1322,1429,1507,1532]" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Lomaspilis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigrita">
<emphasis box="[1322,1429,1507,1532]" italics="true" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">L. nigrita</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which was erected to the species rank by 
<bibRefCitation author="Beljaev, E. A." box="[615,842,1542,1569]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" refId="ref91599" refString="Beljaev, E. A. (2016) Fam. Geometridae - Pyadenitzi. In: Lelei, A. S. (Ed.), Annotated catalogue of the insects of Russian Far East. Vol. 2. Lepidoptera. Dal'nauka, Vladivostok, pp. 518 - 666. [in Russian]" type="book" year="2016">Beljaev (2016: 570)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
